content:
Hey everyone. I was just wondering if there is a channel dedicated to spreading good news about the campaign and victories in general. If not I thought I would suggest it. Maybe once a week HQ could write a post discussing what the campaign and/or our efforts here as volunteers for the campaign have achieved the past week.

Just thought it would be nice to have and really motivating for all of us, as I know it can be easy to lose hope, especially for phonebankers who went through some rough calls.

Hi <@722257413637668944> we have feeds of good news here https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1252676126698897429 and https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1266884554082222142 they are both read-only, but feel free to copy anything and share it anywhere, you can even pull something from there and share it in https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1268690577960992878 to bring more positivity to our community.
